-- Itaú says extends Brazil payroll lender venture with BMG 
-- By Guillermo Parra-Bernal
-- Tue Apr 29, 2014 09:08AM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, April 29 (Reuters) - Itaú Unibanco Holding SA <ITUB4.SA> said on Tuesday it will become Brazil's largest lender of payroll-deductible loans after extending the scope of a joint venture with Banco BMG SA on the segment, according to a securities filing.   (Reporting by Guillermo Parra-Bernal; Editing by Jeffrey Benkoe)  ((guillermo.parra@thomsonreuters.com)(+55-11-5644-7714)(+55-119 -8346-7153)(Reuters Messaging: guillermo.parra.thomsonreuters.com@reuters.net))  Keywords: ITAUUNIBANCO BRAZIL/LOANS

